high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a butter knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple in the sink.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the counter just right of the stove
Pick up the butter knife from the stove
Turn left and walk up to the kitchen sink
Cut the green apple in the sink with the knife
Move over to face the right side of the sink
Put the knife down in the right side of the sink
Move back to face the left side of the sink
Pick up an apple slice from the sink
Turn right and walk over to the microwave on the counter
Heat the apple slice in the microwave and then remove it
Turn around and walk back to the kitchen sink
Put the apple slice in the right side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple slice in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the left sink.
Section the apple in the sink.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the right sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the left hand sink.
Pick up a section of apple from the sink.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Put the apple section in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the right sink.
Put the apple section in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked section of apple into the sink.
